Sample app sinbad
-----------------
    Sinbad OpenNI sample application for Linux

Requirements
------------
    libogre-dev
    libois-dev
    codeblocks
    OpenNI (https://github.com/OpenNI/OpenNI/tree/unstable)
    avin2-sensor (https://github.com/avin2/SensorKinect)
    NITE (http://www.openni.org/Downloads/OpenNIModules.aspx)

Include path
------------
    /usr/include/OGRE
    /usr/include/OIS
    /usr/include/ni
    /usr/include/nite

Original source code repository
-------------------------------
    https://github.com/OpenNI/SampleAppSinbad
    See README.2nd for detail.

